reviews.review_text: SPRING TOUR What a beautiful Spring day it was and what a great way to see the beautiful (Gray Gothic) Duke University for the first time. Blue Devils ... is that an oxymoron? A pretty shade of blue. It matched the sky. It seemed as if time stood still. Thanks for letting me hear it again ... twenty-six years ago!

weird I thought Bobby pulled all soundboards from archive.  Why can we still dl the mp3's of this show (not this version the other 04/02/82)?    Do I have to rate this in order to post my comment....ehhhh they're all five stars.

Grate Times 1st show was Duke 1978. What a wonderful campus. Gorgeous! At this show I finally connected with my future wife and danced all show. Good times. The GD rocked all of 1982. Next day off to Norfolk!
